{"tid":2365303,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政府公布明日全天候開放回港易計劃預約系統","createTime":"2021-01-13T15:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T16:55:56.000Z","uid":32577,"like":4,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c65f6bcbbe62b3f2df74deda3f4fcb16d0cf2cb6","tid":2365303,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T15:26:05.000Z","msg":"政府公布，明天起全天候開放回港易計劃預約系統，方便市民可隨時預約系統內的名額。<br />\n<br />\n在實施新安排後，市民可即時預約1月14日至1月24日的名額。其後預約系統會每逢星期三的零時起，開放下一個星期的7天時段的名額供市民預約，例如市民可由1月20日零時起，預約當天至1月31日的名額。<br />\n<br />\n為實施新的預約安排，回港易計劃的網上預約系統會於明日零時起暫停服務約30分鐘，以進行系統更新。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570270-20210113.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570270-20210113.htm&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuBURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=f1d6521f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570270-20210113.htm&h=0d23188d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570270-20210113.htm</a>"},{"pid":"de5773d762104f044fbe999a42f3c7bb8c4d7adc","tid":2365303,"uid":32577,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T15:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一路屌香港人抗疫疲勞,一路放病毒入黎, CLS"},{"pid":"a4fe3e28958ef73f5b9ef31469f99e324731c3fd","tid":2365303,"uid":58958,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T15:28:12.000Z","msg":"正，攬炒之母"},{"pid":"2da40e44ef5111947c5b632c38e4d54625287baa","tid":2365303,"uid":130709,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T15:29:23.000Z","msg":"第5波is coming to towna"},{"pid":"26a7f5aea0f71c1a81dd5226ebb4e3d707f44fb1","tid":2365303,"uid":114781,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T15:47:00.000Z","msg":"掂，殖民地政府要幫宗主国接收支那肺炎病人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no